'''阿迦汗大學'''（[[烏爾都語|烏爾都語]]：جامىهء ﺁغا خان；{{lang-en|Aga Khan University}}）是一座位於[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]的私立[[研究型大學|研究型大學]]。<ref name="AKU Press">{{cite news|title=Address of AKU|url=http://www.aku.edu/aboutaku/contactus/Pages/default.aspx|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=AKU Press|date=AKU Press|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922022334/http://www.aku.edu/aboutaku/contactus/Pages/default.aspx|archivedate=2013年9月22日}}</ref>大學成立於1983年，其名稱是爲了紀念其資助人[[阿迦汗四世|阿迦汗四世]]。<ref name="University Charter">{{cite web|last=AKU University Press|title=University Charter|url=http://www.aku.edu/aboutaku/leadershipanduniversityadministration/Pages/universitycharter.aspx|work=AKU University Press|publisher=AKU University Press|accessdate=16 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927083934/http://www.aku.edu/aboutaku/leadershipanduniversityadministration/Pages/universitycharter.aspx|archivedate=2013年9月27日}}</ref>

大學主校區在卡拉奇，但在[[東非|東非]]和[[英國|英國]]也有分校。主要提供[[生物科學|生物科學]]和[[醫學|醫學]]相關的本科和研究生課程。巴基斯坦70%的生物醫學研究都來自該大學。<ref name="Ref-2">{{cite web|url=http://www.dawn.com/2007/03/29/local11.htm|title=Need stressed to promote research|accessdate=2007-03-29|archive-date=2008-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212004505/http://www.dawn.com/2007/03/29/local11.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在英國是[[大英國協大學協會|大英國協大學協會]]成員。<ref name="Association of Commonwealth Universities">{{cite news|last=Association of Commonwealth Universities|title=Members of Association of Commonwealth Universities|url=https://www.acu.ac.uk/membership/acu-members/asia-central-south?country_id=172&items_perpage=20&pageID=2|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=Association of Commonwealth Universities|date=Association of Commonwealth Universities|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029203155/https://www.acu.ac.uk/membership/acu-members/asia-central-south?country_id=172&items_perpage=20&pageID=2|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

其醫學領域成就較高，<ref name="HEC press ranking">{{cite web|last=Higher Education Commission|title=HEC ranking|url=http://www.hec.gov.pk/INSIDEHEC/DIVISIONS/QALI/OTHERS/RANKINGOFUNIVERSITIES/Pages/CategoryWise.aspx#|work=Govt. of Pakistan|publisher=HEC press ranking|accessdate=16 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525073744/http://www.hec.gov.pk/InsideHEC/Divisions/QALI/Others/RankingofUniversities/Pages/CategoryWise.aspx|archivedate=2013-05-25}}</ref> 被英國的[[Quacquarelli_Symonds|Quacquarelli Symonds]]評為亞洲前250所大學之一。<ref name="Pakistan Today">{{cite news|last=Staff|title=Six Pakistani universities among top Asian universities: QS Ranking-2012 - See more at: http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2012/05/30/news/national/six-pakistani-universities-among-top-asian-universities-qs-ranking-2012/#sthash.xLWYb3Uu.dpuf|url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2012/05/30/news/national/six-pakistani-universities-among-top-asian-universities-qs-ranking-2012/|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=Pakistan Today|date=30 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627201923/http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2012/05/30/news/national/six-pakistani-universities-among-top-asian-universities-qs-ranking-2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The News Internationale, Islamabad Bureau">{{cite news|last=Imam|first=Myra|title=Three Pakistani universities among top 200 in the world|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-6-184133-Three-Pakistani-universities-among-top-|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=The News Internationale, Islamabad Bureau|date=June 17, 2013|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701125948/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-6-184133-Three-Pakistani-universities-among-top-|dead-url=no}}</ref>

